title: Quotes
---
{#
  ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  This list is driven by content/quotes/quotes.json. JSON can't hold comments,
  so the reference shape lives here (it never renders).

  Fields per entry:
    Required:  text         — the quote body
               attribution  — rendered as "— attribution"

  Both fields support inline Markdown, so links work:
    "Your Name via [X](https://x.com/yourhandle)"

  Reference shape:

      [
        {
          "text": "The quote itself.",
          "attribution": "Author"
        }
      ]
  ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#}
<div class="quotes">
  {% for q in quotes %}
  <blockquote class="quote">
    <p>{{ q.text | mdInline | safe }}</p>
    <cite>— {{ q.attribution | mdInline | safe }}</cite>
  </blockquote>
  {% endfor %}
</div>
